I"B<p>I’ve been working as a video game writer since 2016. Interactive writing has been a huge source of inspiration for me, and I find the game development scene, with its constant strive for innovation, the most exciting place for my craft.</p>

<p>These are the most relevant projects I’ve worked on:</p>

