<h2 id="neighbors">Neighbors</h2>

<p>Visual Novel. Coming to Steam 2022.</p>

<p align="left">
<img src="/content_assets/videogames/neighbors.png" width="500" />
</p>

<h3 id="about-the-project">About the project</h3>

<ul>
  <li><em>Neighbors</em> is a Visual Novel set during the Salem Witch Trials of 1692.</li>
  <li>Based on both the true events and Arthur Miller’s <em>The Crucible</em>, I chose interactive media to retell the story in first person, making player choices deeply conflictive in ethical and moral terms.</li>
  <li>In this project, I was not only the writer but also the owner and creator. I led a team of two artists that created all the original art, and I implemented the writing and the animations using Naninovel and Unity.</li>
</ul>

<p>Visit the game’s <a href="https://store.steampowered.com/app/1857200/Neighbors__A_Visual_Novel/">Steam page</a>.</p>

<p>(<a href="/videogames">back</a>)</p>

